{"type":"message","id":"738bc769","parentId":"1ff53a3b","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:49:50.184Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Fresh start — no memory files yet. USER.md and IDENTITY.md are basically empty. SOUL.md has good guidance on who I should be.\n\nThis is the first conversation. I should be warm but not performative, help set up identity together, and then ask what they want to do.\n\nFeishu DM context means this is a direct message to the user. I should probably ask their name and get started.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey — just came online. Looks like this is a fresh start for both of us. I'm still figuring out who I am, and I don't know your name yet.\n\nWhat should I call you? And what do you want to work on today?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773733471278}}
