{"type":"message","id":"20e776eb","parentId":"b8aa5eeb","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:37:58.783Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 18:37 GMT+8] 400 Total tokens of image and text exceed max message tokens. Request id: sha256:e5ce92098992 这个错误"}],"timestamp":1773743878782}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd9b3424","parentId":"20e776eb","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:38:05.002Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个错误表示 **请求的总 token 数（图片 + 文本）超过了模型允许的最大 message token 限制**。\n\n## 可能的原因：\n1. 你上传了一张太大的图片，图片编码后占用了大量 token\n2. 同时发送了很长的文本提示 + 大图，两者加起来超出了限制\n3. 当前模型的上下文窗口比较小（比如 kimi-k2.5 对长文本/大图的限制）\n\n## 解决方法：\n1. **压缩图片**：降低图片分辨率后再上传\n2. **拆分请求**：如果是多张图片，分批发送\n3. **缩短文本**：简化你的提示词，去掉不必要的描述\n4. **切换模型**：使用上下文窗口更大的模型\n\n你是在什么场景下遇到这个错误的？是分析图片还是编程任务？可以告诉我具体情况，我帮你解决。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773743878783}}
